<Layout title="Store Buy Guides" description="Every in-game store in Last War: Survival — currencies, reset schedules, ranked best buys, and what to never buy in each.">
  <h1>Store Buy Guides</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-[#8a96b0]">Every store, its currency, when it resets, what to buy in what order — and what to skip. Last verified: July 2026.</p>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p><strong>Universal rule:</strong> currencies you can't buy with money (Honor Points, Alliance Coins, Campaign Medals) go to <em>permanent main-squad power</em> — gear blueprints, shards for heroes you actually run, drone parts. Never spend scarce currency on resources or small speedups.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>Cheat Sheet</h2>
  <div class="table-wrapper">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Store</th><th>Reset</th><th>#1 Buy</th><th>Hard Skip</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><strong>Alliance Store</strong></td><td>Weekly (Mon)</td><td>UR Universal Shards</td><td>Resource bundles</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Honor Shop</strong></td><td>Monthly cap, weekly rotation</td><td>ALL Legendary Gear Blueprints</td><td>Gems, resources</td></tr>
